nt|^z@3^b@2^^|cp|8|AT|^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Remember, when you balance you are bidding the entirety of your side's assets, not just your hand. So the weaker you are, the stronger partner is and his points are better positioned.|
