up|32|cp|8|AT|^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|5 level decisions in a competitive auction are probably the most difficult decisions to make. One mistake that most players make is too often they bid "5 over 5" that means they bid to a 5 level contract after the opponents have bid to a 5 level contract.|
